text.data-name: Social Media as Main Information Delivery Channel
text.tspan: Social Media as Main Information Delivery Channel

text.data-name: In 2014, social media has eclipsed search engines as the biggest driver of referral traffic for publishers.
About two-thirds of American adults (68%) say they at least occasionally get news on social media.
Katerina Eva Matsa & Elisa Shearer, Pew Research Center, 2018
Social media has become the main source of news online with more than 2.4 billion internet users.
